      "name": "assay",
      "source": "./assay",
      "description": "Grades every rule in CLAUDE.md and .claude/rules/ — can Claude tell when it fires and what to do? — offers rewrites for the weak ones, flags rules better served by hooks, skills, or subagents, crafts skills that reliably trigger, and interviews you to write rules that stick.",
